import React from 'react'
import Input from '../Input/Input'

                    type='text'
                    name='stgNumber'>

                                id="hasLift"
                                name="hasLift"
                                value="nao"
                            />
                            <label className="property-options"
                            htmlFor="hasLift"
                            children="NÃ£o"/>
            </fieldset>
        </fieldset>
    )
}

export default Complement
